{"tid":573912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清晨闖進立院 1頭部重創急救中","createTime":"2018-02-27T02:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T02:30:06.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7025dc0a873d473c6c05a72a3b321841829d45","tid":573912,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"軍系反年金改革團體「八百壯士」，清晨對立法院發動「突襲」，30多人在駐警攔阻下，成功闖入立法院院區，帶隊的八百壯士副指揮官吳斯懐遭衝撞受傷，由救護車送醫。<br />\n<br />\n退軍今晨的舉措事前保密到家，昨天深夜起，退軍在國民黨立委賴士葆、曾銘宗、費鴻泰等人到場「關切」下進入立法院議場，預計9時發起第二波抗爭。駐警已緊急調派警力來援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/02/27/1/4525748.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F1%2F4525748.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=67e87b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「八百壯士維權護憲指揮部」發出聲明，指退軍於今天清晨5時50分，發動「決戰強力抗爭」，並提出以下訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、立法院立即停止審查『軍人退撫新制』版本修正草案，並與軍系團體代表進行面對面溝通協商。<br />\n二、立即宣布公教警消退撫修正法案暫停實施，並應先聲請釋憲。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說目前軍系退軍正在立法院的現場，呼籲全台的軍公教警消勞北上集結「決戰」。<br />\n<br />\n軍系反年金改革團體「八百壯士」，清晨對立法院發動「突襲」，30多人在駐警攔阻下，仍成功闖入立法院議場，帶隊的八百壯士副指揮官吳斯懐遭衝撞受傷，由救護車送醫<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/02/27/1/4525774.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F1%2F4525774.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=ed48dffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3002017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3002017&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5f2e2fe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3002017</a>"},{"pid":"3c92648c2755e088d6ad01e66661071c63f45c56","tid":573912,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:17:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gPymXXAE3tU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgPymXXAE3tU&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=297f6387\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gPymXXAE3tU</a>"},{"pid":"de827dc558a5d4d36a94172758517267847fe0b8","tid":573912,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:30:06.000Z","msg":"條友死左"}]}